{"tid":1727202,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"識入樽的兔仔破世界健力士紀錄!","createTime":"2019-11-16T11:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:06:40.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ceef615953bc66e110cb93712d5143e968b3ae98","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">識入樽的兔仔破世界健力士紀錄 !</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXNJmeXb4Y0A&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=8c75036e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A</a>"},{"pid":"9869b7d2fd9d52eac2beb42bea46638f261100e2","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢同主人玩：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=6cedcede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"},{"pid":"aab1ae258737b35cedda184689f6f16215939ba6","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢飲水:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=7d745081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a>"},{"pid":"c3ccb1db5575d98dad4934b1f7c7c211543d0fcd","tid":1727202,"uid":208702,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"淮杞兔肉湯<br />\n<br />\n原料：兔肉、淮山藥、枸杞、桂圓、鹽、雞精、料酒、姜。<br />\n<br />\n製法：將兔肉洗凈切成塊；姜切片，山藥切塊待用；坐鍋點火倒入水，放入兔肉、薑片、桂圓、山藥，加入料酒、雞精調味，燉1小時；將枸杞用溫水泡好，開蓋後，加入枸杞改小火再燉半小時，關火後加鹽調味即可食用。<br />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<br />\n功效：滋陰涼血，益氣潤膚，解毒祛熱"},{"pid":"213c9359c0f6b0ac35fdcb3f5849906ab77aed79","tid":1727202,"uid":84998,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3ccb1db5575d98dad4934b1f7c7c211543d0fcd","tid":1727202,"uid":208702,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"淮杞兔肉湯<br />\n<br />\n原料：兔肉、淮山藥、枸杞、桂圓、鹽、雞精、料酒、姜。<br />\n<br />\n製法：將兔肉洗凈切成塊；姜切片，山藥切塊待用；坐鍋點火倒入水，放入兔肉、薑片、桂圓、山藥，加入料酒、雞精調味，燉1小時；將枸杞用溫水泡好，開蓋後，加入枸杞改小火再燉半小時，關火後加鹽調味即可食用。<br />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<br />\n功效：滋陰涼血，益氣潤膚，解毒祛熱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"係人地寵物post貼食譜你覺得好撚好笑？<br />\nOn9仔"},{"pid":"98aa767ec8ba100811a6adeaa21b0844f5306e2b","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養了兔子,瘋狂跳兔子舞!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=f1dd6dc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a>"},{"pid":"860bbc058a3744de87b0803a62f2706088519e56","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">狗狗搶嘢食, 兔兔毫無還擊之力 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子側面看某東西代表正面看某東西，你在牠後面也會看到你。(你可想像正前方是盲點，看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）😭😆🙈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJKwW65LcLIg&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=e63b2ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg</a>"},{"pid":"649100373af21934a9aff513b2dc2b5da42d38ee","tid":1727202,"uid":285444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"213c9359c0f6b0ac35fdcb3f5849906ab77aed79","tid":1727202,"uid":84998,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3ccb1db5575d98dad4934b1f7c7c211543d0fcd","tid":1727202,"uid":208702,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"淮杞兔肉湯<br />\n<br />\n原料：兔肉、淮山藥、枸杞、桂圓、鹽、雞精、料酒、姜。<br />\n<br />\n製法：將兔肉洗凈切成塊；姜切片，山藥切塊待用；坐鍋點火倒入水，放入兔肉、薑片、桂圓、山藥，加入料酒、雞精調味，燉1小時；將枸杞用溫水泡好，開蓋後，加入枸杞改小火再燉半小時，關火後加鹽調味即可食用。<br />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<br />\n功效：滋陰涼血，益氣潤膚，解毒祛熱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"係人地寵物post貼食譜你覺得好撚好笑？<br />\nOn9仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bfaaad369fef2e11a99572f9b2fc2aa43e4014","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子生日Party !!</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NfkeOcEHtOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNfkeOcEHtOk&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=92fdfeff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NfkeOcEHtOk</a>"},{"pid":"9443d3321f40efe1db8f80cc6d001a839a61d22c","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子會不會叫? 是會的....</span></span><br />\n<br />\n開心時會「<span style=\"color: red;\">屋屋</span>」聲叫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPoSiZmzo58&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=b23a0052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿時會<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predator)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=de4ca57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a>"},{"pid":"cdf7e8dea0c4b13838b02d1806464bb2ba16c890","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子食物和份量</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡😊<br />\n- 2湯匙兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙或以下)水果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老兔(6歲以上)：</span><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</span><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養，(而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更多資訊：<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=a4b7ab0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"e295a536d47b6b905fd3c83d8442e0990089e328","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子的睡窩被貓霸佔了 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2HMWjTXFwuY&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=3920ac14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY</a>"},{"pid":"debeae4570338be6f2118070fd5cb1cb69585c12","tid":1727202,"uid":326543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3ccb1db5575d98dad4934b1f7c7c211543d0fcd","tid":1727202,"uid":208702,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"淮杞兔肉湯<br />\n<br />\n原料：兔肉、淮山藥、枸杞、桂圓、鹽、雞精、料酒、姜。<br />\n<br />\n製法：將兔肉洗凈切成塊；姜切片，山藥切塊待用；坐鍋點火倒入水，放入兔肉、薑片、桂圓、山藥，加入料酒、雞精調味，燉1小時；將枸杞用溫水泡好，開蓋後，加入枸杞改小火再燉半小時，關火後加鹽調味即可食用。<br />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<br />\n功效：滋陰涼血，益氣潤膚，解毒祛熱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"試下唔好on9？你媽生你出黎唔係咁用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d2563a576cf2b50d2c2b9613e3c7e2cf21810d","tid":1727202,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子吃西瓜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於糖份高，這video分咗幾日比兔仔食。糖份高不宜多吃，否則損害腸胃，患上致命的GI stasis!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSXw7zGeWMhU&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=f9e60f71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU</a>"}]}